snippet.title: Hollow Knight: Godmaster Release Date Announce
snippet.description:
This August 23rd, experience the final chapter of the knight's journey in Hollow Knight: Godmaster, free for all players on PC & Nintendo Switch.

Godmaster is the final Free Content Pack for Hollow Knight and its largest yet, packed with new bosses, new npcs, new secrets and a whole new mode.

Please note: Hollow Knight: Godmaster is the updated name for the final Free Content Pack.
